AN
ATTEMPT
WAS
MADE
RECENTLY
AT
THE
NAVAL
ORDNANCE
LABORATORY
TO
ESTABLISH
A
UNIQUE
RELATIONSHIP
BETWEEN
GIVEN
LOCAL
FLOW
CONDITIONS
AT
